LICENSE NOTICE
==============

This repository is currently in Phase 0 (Foundation) development. The
final license has not yet been determined. The intent, per
docs/ARCHITECTURE.md §1.4, is an "open core" model:

  - Processing engine (Rust core, src-tauri/src/): MIT or Apache-2.0
  - Frontend UI (src/): to be determined, likely MIT or Apache-2.0
  - Pro plugins and commercial extensions: proprietary

Until the license is finalized:

  - You may read, fork, and study the source for evaluation purposes.
  - You may NOT redistribute, modify, or incorporate this code into
    other products without explicit written permission from the author.
  - Contributions accepted via PR are accepted under the same tentative
    terms — by submitting a PR you agree to license your contribution
    under whatever final license MetaRDU Industrial adopts.

Contact: open an issue at https://github.com/error302/metardu-industrial/issues
for licensing questions.
